GoverningSphereSpec.Label: Work
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: Something I can do; something I know; or something I am.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Work
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Earn a living, or practice the invisible arts.

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: Explore
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: A place; a person; a location; a secret.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Explore
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Explore the city with Health or Followers; explore locations; or investigate the possibilities of lore. Exploration is often unpredictable.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Read this volume of Travelling at Night
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: 'The Wood lies outside the walls of the Mansus. As any student of Histories knows, the Mansus has no walls.'

GoverningSphereSpec.Label: Dream
GoverningSphereSpec.Description: A direction for my dreams; or a trouble to recover from.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Dream
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Rest; reconsider your priorities; or risk yourself in exploration of the kingdoms of sleep.

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: Bleak Thoughts
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Dark days. I must be careful not to let doubts creep in. [Dread may provoke full-fledged Despair.]

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: DESPAIR
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Despair is the wolf that devours thought. [You can defeat Despair by feeding it Contentment; otherwise, it will destroy you when it reaches 3 Dread.]

Illuminations.tlg.notes.title: DESPAIR
Illuminations.tlg.notes.description: Despair pads close at my heels. The world is leached of light. [You can defeat Despair by feeding it Contentment; otherwise, it will destroy you when it reaches 3 Dread.]
